ZH: 若不下雨，我们就去爬山。
EN: If it doesn't rain, we will go mountain climbing.

ZH: 若不努力学习，你就不能进入理想的大学。
EN: If you don't study hard, you won't be able to get into your ideal university.

ZH: 若不早点出发，我们会错过飞机。
EN: If we don't leave early, we will miss the plane.

ZH: 若不及时修理，这台机器就会坏掉。
EN: If it's not repaired in time, this machine will break.

ZH: 若不及时处理，这个问题就会变得更糟。
EN: If it's not dealt with promptly, this problem will become worse.

ZH: 若不好好休息，你会很快感到疲劳。
EN: If you don't rest properly, you will quickly feel fatigued.

ZH: 若不小心碰到，你会受伤的。
EN: If you accidentally touch it, you will get hurt.

ZH: 若不现在改变，你将来会后悔的。
EN: If you don't change now, you will regret it in the future.

ZH: 若不找到解决方案，这个困扰会一直存在。
EN: If a solution is not found, this problem will persist.

ZH: 若不足够谨慎，你会犯同样的错误。
EN: If you're not careful enough, you will make the same mistake.

ZH: 若不好好管理时间，你会无法完成任务。
EN: If you don't manage your time well, you won't be able to complete the task.

ZH: 若不小心摔伤了，你要及时处理伤口。
EN: If you accidentally get injured, you need to treat the wound promptly.

ZH: 若不尽快解决，这个纠纷会变得很复杂。
EN: If it's not resolved soon, this dispute will become very complicated.

ZH: 若不小心打碎了，你需要赔偿。
EN: If you accidentally break it, you need to compensate.

ZH: 若不停下来，你会迷路的。
EN: If you don't stop, you will get lost.

ZH: 若不好好照顾植物，它们会枯萎的。
EN: If you don't take good care of the plants, they will wither.

ZH: 若不赶快学会游泳，你将无法参加比赛。
EN: If you don't learn how to swim quickly, you won't be able to participate in the competition.

ZH: 若不及时维修，车辆会变得不安全。
EN: If not repaired promptly, the vehicle will become unsafe.

ZH: 若不打开窗户，房间会变得闷热。
EN: If you don't open the windows, the room will become stuffy.

ZH: 若不做好准备，你会失败的。
EN: If you're not prepared, you will fail.
